data.description: This beautifully appointed 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts a convenient location within 5 minutes of Fort Carson and I-25. Upon entry, a flexible space can be utilized as a living room or home office, with a modern barn door leading to a conveniently located and upgraded half-bathroom. The open floor plan seamlessly transitions into the expansive living area, ideal for entertaining. The gourmet kitchen features stunning granite countertops and upgraded appliances, perfect for any chef.  An adjoining spacious dining area provides easy access to the back patio, perfect for indoor/outdoor living. Upstairs, a large loft area offers additional living space. French doors lead into the luxurious primary suite, complete with a spa-like 5-piece master bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet.  The two secondary bedrooms each feature ample closet space, providing comfortable accommodations for family or guests. This meticulously maintained home is ready for you to move in and create lasting memories.
